@KeycloakLab3_HostAddress = http://localhost:5276

### 1. Public endpoint (no token)
GET {{KeycloakLab3_HostAddress}}/public
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Protected endpoint (any valid token)
GET {{KeycloakLab3_HostAddress}}/protected
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### 3. GET /reports — requires reports:read scope
GET {{KeycloakLab3_HostAddress}}/reports
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### 4. POST /reports — requires reports:write scope
POST {{KeycloakLab3_HostAddress}}/reports
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###
